cs.DB, cs.PL, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS

The paper presents a coordination language for distributed database applications, which suggests that it belongs to the database (cs.DB) and programming languages (cs.PL) sub-categories. The language also deals with distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE) aspects, as well as data structures (cs.DS) such as tables.
